defaultThe
default 
defaultCommunications Act sets the purposes of public service broadcasting:
default(a)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultthe provision of relevant television services which secure that 
defaultprogrammes dealing with a wide range of subject-matters are made available for viewing;
default(b)
