defaultthe provision of relevant television services in a manner which (having regard to the days on which they are shown and the times of day at which they are shown) is 
defaultlikely to meet the needs and satisfy the interests of as many different audiences as practicable;
default(c)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultthe provision of relevant television services which (taken together and having regard to the same matters) are properly balanced, so far as their nature and s
defaultubject-matters are concerned, for meeting the needs and satisfying the interests of the available audiences; and
default(d)
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultthe provision of relevant television services which (taken together) maintain high general standards with respect to the programmes included in
default them, and
default, in particular with respect to:
default&#xa0;
default3.16
default              
defaultThe public service broadcasting objectives are
default intended to ensure that programming is provided that, among other things: disseminates information; is educational and entertaining; reflects cultural diversity; covers news and current affairs; provides coverage of sporting events; includes topics such a
defaults science and religion; and includes high quality and original programmes for children and young people.
